channel.name: Geek Community
channel.description: This is a channel that i am creating in the hopes of gathering a Geek Community. A place where like minded people can gather together to share ideas, find help with projects, ask questions, and collaborate on projects. Explore the depths of technology, discover new ideas, and work together to create new things.

topic.title: Looking for Geek/Nerd minded people to create a Geek Community group.
topic.body:
I am look for people with varying skills to create a Geek Community where everyone can share ideas, collaborate on projects, and work together to achieve a common goal. This group will be member driven which means there will be no central leader; everyone will make their own decisions and will help to moderate the community. If anyone is interested in this please feel free to drop a comment or you can mail me on Zeromail @redneck

thank you and I hope to see this group.
